      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Crocus was a young mortal, who was in love with the Nymph Smilax. Either
        the love was not returned, or no love was possible between mortal and nymph,
        leading to the gods taking pity upon Crocus, turning him into the saffron
        flower as a relief for his grief."

'
